721a8-c70b-47ce-9e6b-4e0b3341d448 grids-is-advanced\"><div class=\"grids-s-w_i\">\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-21a5c99a-2d73-46bc-bfb6-be193a381339\">\n\n<p class=\"is-style-preheader has-text-color\" style=\"color:#066756\">USE CASE<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3>Give Relevant Shipping Information<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Unexpected shipping costs are among the top reasons for cart abandonment. Inform visitors of your delivery options\u2014specifically for their country.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Set expectations for when their packages will arrive at their country or promote your country-specific shipping offers.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-1d79411d-7ff7-4bd7-9090-e5efb36675ae\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-2-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-115858\" width=\"365\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-2-1.png 730w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-2-1-282x300.png 282w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-2-1-380x404.png 380w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-2-1-600x638.png 600w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-2-1-33x35.png 33w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-2-1-47x50.png 47w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-2-1-461x490.png 461w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-2-1-220x234.png 220w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-2-1-385x409.png 385w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 365px) 100vw, 365px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n<div  class=\"grids-section grids-s-022a3189-7266-4538-92ec-eae73c034ab7 grids-is-advanced\"><div class=\"grids-s-w_i\">\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-929e9068-9a0f-4f2e-9cb6-7f25fab8fe8d\">\n\n<p class=\"is-style-preheader has-text-color\" style=\"color:#066756\">USE CASE<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3>Grow a Segmented Email List<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Your winter collection may not be relevant for Australian visitors in January. Your offers in London may not be a big hit in Paris.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Personalize your popup copy dynamically with the visitor&#8217;s location and attract only relevant subscribers.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"grids-area grids-a-e663a623-5a4f-4286-b1b7-37cb66b09088\">\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/sleeknote.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-3-1024x693.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-115859\" width=\"511\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-3-1024x693.png 1024w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-3-300x203.png 300w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Geo-targeting-3-768x520.png 768w, https:\/\/n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\/wp-content\